title: New Jersey Firm Expands Recall of Ground Beef Products Due To Possible Adulteration
summary: Editor's Note: This recall release is being reissued to expand the January 10 recall to include an undetermined amount of additional ground beef products. WASHINGTON, Jan. 14, 2011 - One Great Burger, an Elizabeth, N.J., establishment, is expanding its Jan. 10, 2011 recall to include...
impacted_products: 4 lbs. boxes of "Winn Dixie beef patty 100% BEEF." Each box contains 16 frozen patties weighing ¼ lb. each
